					<p>Hi Claudia!  IF you turn on music and your Furby starts dancing, then he hears sound.  I suggest playing with the Furby for a few days and see if it starts working better. Sometimes it just takes a little bit of time.   With your Samsung Galaxy,  remove the app and re-install it and when you run the Furby App, make sure the phone is pointing at your Furby.   If after a week you still don&#8217;t feel that Furby is working properly you should return it to the store and exchange it for a different one.</p>

