			<div class="comment-box">
			
				<div class="comment-author">
					<strong>admin</strong>
					<small>September 24, 2013 at 12:58 am</a> - <a class='comment-reply-link' href='/troubleshooting-your-furby/?replytocom=616#respond' onclick='return addComment.moveForm("-616", "616", "respond", "167")'>Reply</a></small>
				</div>
			
				<div class="comment-text">
					
					<p>Play it a song and make sure the music is loud enough that Furby can hear it.  If he still wont move or dance, try resetting it.  If it still wont move properly, you should take it back to the store and exchange it (did you save the receipt?).    Usually the reset alone will fix most problems, although sometimes it takes more than one reset to get it right.</p>

				</div>
			
