				</div>
			
				<div class="comment-text">
					
					<p>Are you using an iphone or iPad? if so, after the Ios7 update (on Apple devices) You need to give the app access to your microphone.  – (Settings – Privacy – Microphone – Furby App – Select On.). The app on your apple device makes a sound that humans usually don’t hear, that is how it “talks” to the Furby.  Let me know if this works!</p>

