				</div>
			
				<div class="comment-text">
					
					<p>If you have a problem with your furby&#8217;s sleeping, then you shouldn&#8217;t leave him/her on his/her side. If your waking up a furby with sleeping problems, then you should try waking up the furby on his/her feet. If he/she is woken up on his/her side, then he/she will only stay awake for a few seconds.</p>

				</div>
			
			</div>
			
		</div>

